        "text": " (Revised Version, with even the Received Text). ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "Answered and said unto them",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". He makes no verbal self-defence, but appeals to the effects of his work. Observe that a similar appeal to effects of the same character as those mentioned here - restoration to normal powers and bringing spiritual truths home to the poorest - is still the great argument for the Messiahship of Jesus. ",
        "children": []
